## Language model agnostic

Stencila uses the best agent for the job, for every job

In the fast-paced world of AI, keeping up with the latest and greatest models can be a daunting task. Stencila removes this complexity by regularly benchmarking a variety of AI models to ensure optimal performance. For every task you undertake, Stencila automatically selects the best-suited model, saving you time and effort. Focus on your scientific writing and research‚Äîwe'll handle the heavy lifting of choosing the right AI tool to enhance your work.


